



A) Do the following using Reflection

1) create a class library calculator
2) Create a read and write property number of double type.
3) add a method cube() & calculate cube using the number property created above
4) add a method sqrt(double number) & write logic to calculate squareRoot


B) Do the following using Custom Attributes

1) create a custom attribute called StereoDisc which has songname,language,lyrics properties.
2) Apply the above attribute to a class Song
3) Fetch Custom attributes applied to the class.